---
title: Grilled Spicy Caribbean Tofu Salad  with Jerk Sweet Potatoes and Corn
description: This salad is bringing the Island flavour. Corn, roasted sweet potato and crunchy cucumbers are tossed in a creamy sriracha dressing, then eaten with a spicy Jerk seasoned tofu for a meal that truly kicks things up a notch.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R1007_W31_CA_RC24016-1_Main_low-38d7dd45.jpg
